@startuml
|User|
start
:Login via GitHub;
:Select Repository;

|Git Auth Service|
:Check Sync Status;
if (Need Sync?) then (yes)
    :Fetch File Tree;
    :Push File Events to Kafka;
else (no)
    :Return Cached Data;
endif

|Kafka Queue|
:Queue "repo-files-processing";

|Repo Parser Service|
:Consume Event;
:Parse AST;
:Store Graph (Neo4j);
:Generate Summary (Gemini);
:Update Status (MySQL);

|User|
:View Analysis Results;
stop
@enduml
